"Simulate random date fetch delays" = "Simulasikan penundaan acak saat mengambil tanggal";
"Debug" = "Debug";
"When enabled, each date fetch is delayed by a random duration between 0 and twice the timeout. If the random delay exceeds the timeout, the fetch is aborted as if a timeout occurred." = "Saat diaktifkan, setiap pengambilan tanggal ditunda selama durasi acak antara 0 hingga dua kali waktu tunggu. Jika penundaan acak melampaui waktu tunggu, pengambilan dibatalkan seperti saat waktu habis.";
